column2: Nestlé India Limited manufactures and sells food products in India. The company offers milk products and nutrition
column8: and health care nutrition products; prepared dishes and cooking aids
column13: and cereals; powdered and liquid beverages comprises instant coffee and tea
column14: and ready to drink beverages; and confectionery products
column17: and sugar confectionery products. It also offers vending systems and food services. The company also exports its products. Nestlé India Limited was incorporated in 1959 and is headquartered in Gurugram
